{"tid":199870,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"重睇左大逃殺2,搵唔到特別篇,是否悲哀?","createTime":"2017-04-13T13:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T09:25:14.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05b112cd9c1d994f28360a12a5f2e74890d81953","tid":199870,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:33:52.000Z","msg":"SEED: <a href=\"http://www.xl720.com/thunder/8536.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xl720.com%2Fthunder%2F8536.html&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=9b850b2f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xl720.com/thunder/8536.html</a><br />\n注意唔係特別篇黎<br />\n<br />\n其實套野都拍得幾差,可能因為子承父業,上集導演拍左一個場景就死左,個仔中途接手尾<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%83%E6%AE%BA2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2580%2583%25E6%25AE%25BA2&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2af6045b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%83%E6%AE%BA2</a><br />\nWIKI有詳細講<br />\n差響邊呢?我覺得最難忍受係搖鏡用太多,睇到有D頭暈,為左拍戰爭場面果種激烈感而搖鏡,可惜OVER左,<br />\n本來角色人數多,D裝束又差唔多,鏡頭仲要係咁搖,令觀眾更加難去分清邊個打邊個<br />\n仲有個狂躁症MK主角好惡頂,郁D就大吵大鬧,好煩膠"},{"pid":"84c97056d4233f450987467853609cc5d61cfd27","tid":199870,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47ba4oQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47ba4oQ.gif&h=da613148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/329Pa2F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F329Pa2F.gif&h=acd0915a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5f146cf711c1f04a92b6995f4711a4cfaac3ef1","tid":199870,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"1&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;2"},{"pid":"1a869804d75ec189021199e4dcff0458feb47155","tid":199870,"uid":49391,"like":0,